title: Standard Pass
description: Includes standard entry to theme park and all rides. Only for 3 hours.

title: Classic Pass
description: A full day pass in addition to the Standard Pass benefits.

title: Fast track Pass
description: An upgrade to the Classic Pass to include fast track entry into rides.

title: Purple pack Pass
description: An upgrade to the Classic Pass to include a free meal at any of our restaurants. (one time use)

title: Full bundle Pass
description: A full bundle pass including a meal and fast track. You wouldn't need anything else!

title: Premium Pass
description: Only for our biggest patrons. Full inclusive deal.
